Casual / Bar Yes you can still go out in Manhattan for under $10 and have drinks and some amazingly decent grub. YUM YUM YUM These burgers are thick and prepared exactly how you like them.  Rarely an empty seat in the house -- this tiny little "corner" bistro serves up exactly what all the reviewers say, one heck of a burger and a beer!  It's good and worth the trip. Romance Factor:  4 Hobnob Potential:  6 Destination Rating:  9 Strong suggestions: Bistro Burger, and anything that is on tap.
